    {
      "text": "The sample comprises the 103 largest stock exchange-listed insurers globally. The top quartile comprises 25 companies: 4 in EMEA, 14 in the Americas, and 7 in APAC. Components of TSR are multiplicative but converted and shown here as additive, ",
      "x": 81.8,
      "y": 542.9,
      "w": 1062.4,
      "h": 13.0,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Light",
      "size": 10.0,
      "color": "#717172",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "with remainders assigned to the multiple change field. Aggregation is based on market capitalization weights at the start of the period. TSR is calculated in each company’s reporting currency. TBV = tangible book value of equity without OCI (other ",
      "x": 53.4,
      "y": 555.9,
      "w": 1050.2,
      "h": 13.0,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Light",
      "size": 10.0,
      "color": "#717172",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
